{"tid":1721921,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如何對抗蛇齋餅粽","createTime":"2019-11-14T19:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T19:41:31.000Z","uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c483e517c1aac5f0a7a2d4887a9f2d886ecc3db0","tid":1721921,"uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:39:05.000Z","msg":"之前開過，不過p牌推唔倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信大家屋企都有廢老收左蛇齋餅粽去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老一輩覺得收左人嘅禮物就要幫返人，呢樣野我地改變唔倒<br />\n但係我地可以做嘅係利用佢地另一樣改變唔倒嘅野<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">貪念<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n我地只要同啲廢老解釋返奶共班狗派野嘅目的就係要贏選舉，而佢地輸左嘅話嚟緊幾年就會派更多野想贏返下次選舉，咁班貪心嘅廢老就會自動波唔投奶共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁多位孝順嘅子孫唔係唔幫手呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵人幫我推呀唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577104c20c32b7266b280aec02dfb4160a8259cb","tid":1721921,"uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:39:44.000Z","msg":"人嚟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aac2fdce9d24cd39d122d9952b4cc74bbae3bc8","tid":1721921,"uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:41:31.000Z","msg":"下次開創意台先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}